{"word":"Abishai","slug":"abishai","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Abishai</b> <a href=\"#/H52\">H52</a> <br/> Son of Zeruiah, David's sister<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=16'>1Ch 2:16</a><br/> One of David's chief men<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=18'>2Sa 23:18</a><br/> Seeks Saul's life<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=26&verse=8'>1Sa 26:8</a><br/> Pursues and slays Abner<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=2&verse=24'>2Sa 2:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=30'>2Sa 3:30</a><br/> Defeats the Edomites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=18&verse=12'>1Ch 18:12</a><br/> Defeats the Ammonites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=10'>2Sa 10:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=14'>2Sa 10:14</a><br/> Seeks the life of Shimei<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=16&verse=9'>2Sa 16:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=19&verse=21'>2Sa 19:21</a><br/> Leads a division of David's army against Absalom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=2'>2Sa 18:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=5'>2Sa 18:5</a><br/> Overthrows Sheba<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=20&verse=22'>2Sa 20:22</a><br/> Saves David from being slain by a Philistine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=21&verse=17'>2Sa 21:17</a><br/> Obtains water from the well of Bethlehem for David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=11&verse=20'>1Ch 11:20</a>"}]}